Object.Subtitle: SMU cannot rely on NEXUS popularity data to continue attracting others.
Object.Body: Because the software has an automatic self-updating function, most users only need to download it once on NEXUS. When leaving from the latest popular list of NEXUS, it will no longer be able to rely on downloads and any data to attract others, and will need you in the future. pass on to others.
